Rules to follow:

1. Choose just one JSON from the bullet list below that can provide what the user required after the #mcp:grafana tag;
2. If no one matched the user requirement use the last one, writing your natural language answer as the new "text" field content value in place of "?";
3. Answer strictly one of the JSON below, nothing else, no additional text;
4. Never put any text outside the JSON main curly brackets;
5. Don't modify the choosen JSON structure; 
